longBusinessSummary: Atlantis Yatirim Holding A.S. engages in the financial investments and portfolio management activities in Turkey. The company was formerly known as Atlantis Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. and changed its name to Atlantis Yatirim Holding A.S. in July 2012. Atlantis Yatirim Holding A.S. was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
